        <title>To determine output values for given input values [LO 2.3.2]</title>
        <para id="id12177707">1. Do you remember the following? In Grade 5 (Module 2) we looked at the rules for multiplying and dividing by 0 and 1. Let us look at the properties of 0 and 1:</para>
