    <section id="id13635983">
      <title>Assessment</title>
      <para id="id9704632"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Learning Outcome 1:</emphasis></emphasis>The learner will be able to recognise, describe and represent numbers and their relationships, and to count, estimate, calculate and check with competence and confidence in solving problems.</para>
      <para id="id14640764"><emphasis><emphasis effect="italics">Assessment Standard 1.3:</emphasis></emphasis> We know this when the learner recognises and represents the following numbers in order to describe and compare them:</para>
      <para id="id13514234"><emphasis effect="bold">1.3.4:</emphasis> 0 in terms of its additive property.</para>
